name: Cheese & Music
description:
Every Friday from June to the beginnig of October, the ErlebnisSennerei Dairy Zillertal invites you to join them for a pleasant afternoon with music! During the summer months, Zillertal music groups perform every Friday from 3.00 to 6.00 p.m. at the ErlebnisSennerei in Mayrhofen.
